    From the W3C CEDDL specification:

    This object describes the component.

     digitalData.component[n].<b>componentInfo</b> = {
 		<b>componentID:</b> "rog300v",
 		componentName: "How to Use Rogaine",
 		description: "Hair Treatment Video"
 	};
